name: Burn Em All
description:
The furious townsfolk watch in glee as Mad King GM, tied to his stake, went up in flames, the glee soon turned to horror as the King laughed manically as the flames engulfed his body

The people of Glitchville realised that the legend of old was true.. royal blood does not burn

As the laughing King stepped from the fire, the townsfolk one by one dropped to their knees begging forgiveness

Then as the as the final rebel leader bent the knee the King looked at them and screamed 3 words 

BURN EM ALL!!!
